dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Elizabeth, New Jersey, volume two : Union Township, Hillside Township, Roselle and Roselle Park, Linden Borough and Linden Township
dct_description_sm: Includes key, key map, streets and specials index, and text. "5562." Hillside Township, Union Township, Roselle and Roselle Park, and Linden Borough and Linden Township have separate title sheets (sheets 224, 238, 300 and 328); each sheet has title, key, key map, streets and specials index, and text.
